text: Lisa Scheibert (born 22 September 1963) is a Norwegian rower. She competed in the women's single sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Norway Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Washington, D.C.
